<main>  
  <div class="container center-align">
    <span id="character-id" data-id="{{user.id}}"></span>
    <div class="row">
      <br/>
      <h1 id="landing-title" class="col s12 page-title">ROAD TO ROME</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-content-box z-depth-5">

      <div class="row">
        <h5 id="landing-subheader" class="col s12">Do you have what it takes to defeat the Empire's greatest champions?</h5>
        <div class="col s12">
          <p>
            The time is Third Century A.D. and the Roman Empire is at its greatest extent. To celebrate his latest conquest, the Emperor Trajan has announced the most glorious gladitorial games to date set to take place over more than 100 days. Aspiring heroes dream of riches, fame, glory and freedom. Sharpen your weapons, don your armor and hone your skills. Hail, Emperor! Those about to die salute you. This is the Road to Rome.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        {{#if isloggedin}}
          <a href="/ludus-magnus"><button id="post-item" class="landing-btn col s4 btn btn-large">Ludus Magnus</button></a>
          <a href="/accounts/view"><button class="landing-btn col s4  btn btn-large">View Account</button></a>
          <a href="/logout"><button type="btn" class="landing-btn col s4 btn btn-large">Save + Logout</button></a>
        {{else}}
          <button class="col s6 btn btn-large modal-trigger" href="#account-info">SIGN-IN</button>
          <button id="sign-up" class="col s6 btn btn-large">SIGN-UP</button>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
